des:
Listen to Fox News Radio, the daily Fox News Rundown, and all of the Fox News podcasts.

Once you've enabled the Fox News skill say, "Alexa, open Fox News," to get started. You can also try saying the following:

Alexa, play Fox News.
Alexa, ask Fox News for the latest news.
Alexa, tell Fox News to give me the news.
Alexa, ask Fox News for the news.
Alexa, ask Fox News to play the Radio. 
Alexa, tell Fox News to play the Hemmer Time podcast.
Alexa, ask Fox News to play The Brian Kilmeade Show.
Alexa, tell Fox News to play The Five.
